  "page": "Damon Lannister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Damon Lannister</b> has been the name of multiple members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(Lord)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Damon Lannister (Lord)\">Damon Lannister</a>, known as the <b>Grey Lion</b>, a Lord of Casterly Rock.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)\" title=\"Damon Lannister (son of Jason)\">Damon Lannister</a>, eldest son of Ser Jason Lannister,  older brother to Joanna and Stafford Lannister.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Damon_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Damion_Lannister\" title=\"Damion Lannister\">Damion Lannister</a>, a knight of House Lannister, cousin to the main branch.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403182102\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18678-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403182102 and revision id 279695\n -->\n",
